messages.title: Save Our Sure Start
messages.content: Having spoken to Ian at length I am convinced that our children's future will only be safe under a Labour Government. My daughters benefited from Sure Start and I want the best for our community and as the Tories say they will close our Sure Start Centre and I am not prepared to take that risk. We need Sure Start and only a Labour Government will keep it safe.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: A commitment to keeping Sure Start centers open, in opposition to the Tory proposal of closing them.

issues.socialWelfare: Labour Government will keep Sure Start centers safe.

endorsements.endorsement: Kizzy Fawcett, a Beverley parent, endorses Ian, stating that she believes children's future is only safe under a Labour Government.

images.caption: Kizzy Fawcett, a Beverley Parent, supporting Labour's commitment to Sure Start centers.
